---
import Icons from "./Icons.astro"
---

<section
    id="inicio"
    class="h-screen flex flex-col justify-center items-center px-4 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto"
>
    <div class="space-y-4 flex flex-col items-center">
        <h1 class="text-[clamp(2rem,5vw,3.5rem)] font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 via-purple-500 to-pink-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent animate-fade-in">
            Bryan Soria Méndez
        </h1>

        <h2 class="text-[clamp(1.2rem,3vw,2rem)] font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-red-400 to-red-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent drop-shadow-lg animate-fade-in delay-200">
            Desarrollador de software
        </h2>

        <div class="bg-slate-900/70 backdrop-blur-sm p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-700/50 shadow-md animate-slide-up">
            <p class="text-slate-300 text-[clamp(0.9rem,2vw,1.1rem)] leading-relaxed">
                Tengo un año de experiencia como freelance en aplicaciones web, móviles y de escritorio híbridas. 
                Cada vez que aprendo algo nuevo y complejo de entender, lo escribo en artículos para explicar esos conceptos de manera más sencilla para los demás ✍️.
            </p>
        </div>

        <Icons
            sectionClass="flex justify-center items-center gap-4 animate-fade-in delay-400"
            iconClass="w-[clamp(1.8rem,4vw,2rem)] h-[clamp(1.8rem,4vw,2rem)] hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-200"
        />

        <a 
            href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1uTVbDWVizg0t_fC8lDNEg3qcRxqERuyD/view?usp=drive_link" 
            target="_blank" 
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="cv-btn flex items-center gap-2 mt-3"
        >
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 16v2a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2v-2M7 10l5 5m0 0l5-5m-5 5V4" />
            </svg>
            Abrir CV
        </a>

    </div>
</section>

<style>
    @keyframes fadeIn {
        0% { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
        100% { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
    .animate-fade-in { animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-out forwards; }
    .delay-200 { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
    .delay-400 { animation-delay: 0.4s; }

    @keyframes slideUp {
        0% { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(40px); }
        100% { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
    .animate-slide-up { animation: slideUp 0.9s ease-out forwards; }

    .cv-btn {
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #6d28d9, #db2777);
        color: white;
        font-weight: 700;
        padding: 10px 24px;
        border-radius: 9999px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: clamp(0.9rem,2vw,1rem);
        box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .cv-btn:hover {
        transform: translateY(-2px) scale(1.05);
        box-shadow: 0 5px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
    }
</style>
